Level_Description_13_C4793EFF4D84EB7389B.SourceString: Wide open black and purple room for rent!
Deep down the magestic Cyber sewer system, this is what we found! Fantastic location for some great Zed-Mayhem!
Welcome to the Planetarium! A base placed on a random planet seems like a good place for some Blood and Gore, am I right?
The future is upon us! The year is 2077 and everything is Neon and shit. Go for a walk in the city, fluke some Zeds and have a Zed-Cola!
This Tram station was used by the citizens for commuting to random locations. Nowadays it is used as zed hunting by people like you.
Step inside the largest Aquarium in Zedfest Universe! Take a look at the beautiful fish, or try out one of the wonderful water slides!
Welcome to Zanta's Wonderful Winterland! Lots of Snow, Gingerbread cookies and igloos! There might even be a Christmas present for you found somewhere on the map!
